  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Multi-Tool</span>. This brightly-coloured rifle offers the user cutting-edge defensive capabilities in ground combat situations.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Take</span> this Multi-Tool to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current Multi-Tool. Swap between active Multi-Tools from the Utilities section of the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一台专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">多用途工具</span>。这把颜色艳丽的步枪能够在地面战环境中为使用者提供顶尖的防御能力。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收下</span>这个多用途工具，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的多用途工具<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中的工具部分切换可用的多用途工具。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">工具組</span>。這種顏色明亮的步槍在地面作戰時，會為使用者提供最尖端的防禦能力。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">取走</span>這個工具組以加入你的收藏，或是與目前工具組<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，利用快捷選單（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中的機能頁面切換使用中的工具組。"
  },
